block.minium_me.easy_grinder.desc: If Mobs step on it, the Mobs take %.f damage. This causes the killed Mob to lose experience, but not the loot from the player's kill.
block.minium_me.advanced_grinder.desc: If Mobs step on it, the Mobs take %.0f damage. Mob killed by this will drop experience and loot from the player's kill.
item.minium_me.deepslate_miner.desc: Capable of destroying deepslate and tuff in a 5x5x5 area in one lump sum. It will be gone after one use.
item.minium_me.wind_exploder.desc: It creates a blast at your feet. If you are gliding, you can fly in the direction you are headed, but be careful not to collide with it.
item.minium_me.advanced_wind_exploder.de: Improved Wind Exploder. Enchantable with Unbreaking and Mending. And shorter cool time.
item.minium_me.smithing_template.minium_: Add Chainmail Armor, Minium Tool, Weapon
item.minium_me.smithing_template.iris_qu: Add Concentrated Minium Armor, Tool, Weapon, Iris Quartz ChestPlate
Add Iris Quartz Ingot(When update Iris Quartz ChestPlate, Add Iris Quartz Elytra)
Concentrated Minium Armor, Tool, Weapon, Iris Quartz ChestPlate
Iris Quartz Ingot(When update Iris Quartz ChestPlate, Iris Quartz Elytra)
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_multitool.des: By Double-right-clicking on a stone-based block while sneaking, you can destroy all stone-based blocks in a 7x7x7 area at once.
Gain Poison Heal Effect and Prevent fall damage and collision damage.
When you die, you consume and revive, but a minute cooldown is imposed.
If you fall into the void, in dimensions with a ceiling you will respawn at the spawn point, and in dimensions without a ceiling you will be granted Slow Falling and warped to a high location.
Some effects are enhanced, Reduce damage except for certain parts and Prevent wither damage when wearing a full set of Iris Quartz equipment.
item.minium_me.energy.type.error.desc: There is invalid energy. Use for reset.
item.minium_me.energy.type.empty.desc: There is no energy in it. Hold the gun in your main hand and the ore in your off hand and use it while sneaking to load it.
item.minium_me.energy.type.coal.desc: Fire attribute attack. Note that it cannot damage mobs that are resistant to the fire attribute.
item.minium_me.energy.type.copper.desc: It has the same power as iron, but costs twice as much. If copper energy is used from the block, this block may be weathered or waxed.
item.minium_me.energy.type.gold.desc: It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.lapis.desc: Random effects are applied to mobs that are hit.
item.minium_me.energy.type.redstone.desc: Slightly shorter cool time and reduce the invincibility time of a hit mob opponent. It also installs energy that emits redstone power at the point of impact.
item.minium_me.energy.type.diamond.desc: More powerful than other ores and gems.It is even more powerful against bosses.
item.minium_me.energy.type.emerald.desc: Note that the attack will go through against mobs that disable flying tools, but will be repelled against Breeze.
item.minium_me.energy.type.quartz.desc: Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.glowstone.des: It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light. When it lands on a block, it leaves a glowstone light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.netherite.des: It is very powerful and can also give Wither effect.
item.minium_me.energy.type.amethyst.desc: Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.c_minium.desc: It is as powerful as Netherite.
item.minium_me.energy.type.osmium.desc: More powerful than steel. It has the additional effect of poisoning.
item.minium_me.energy.type.iris_quartz.d: It is very powerful but has the worst cost performance.
item.minium_me.energy.type.source_gem.de: When it hits an enemy, it gives a random favorable effect to the player who shot it. Shooting at tame mobs can restore their health.
item.minium_me.energy.type.aluminium.des: Easy to shoot continuously and reduce the invincibility time of a hit mob opponent.
item.minium_me.energy.type.lead.desc: It has the additional effect of poisoning.
item.minium_me.energy.type.tin.desc: Increases damage to mobs touching water.
item.minium_me.energy.type.uranium.desc: Significantly increased damage against Illager, Villager and Player.
item.minium_me.energy.type.zinc.desc: When it stops, satiety is restored for a short period of time with a certain probability.
item.minium_me.energy.type.bronze.desc: It has high firepower and ignores flying tools, but like copper, it is one shot for two ores, so fuel consumption is not good.
item.minium_me.energy.type.steel.desc: It has the effect of setting the target on fire, and while it is burning, the damage increases, but it is not effective against Mobs that are resistant to fire. It is also less powerful against Mobs who are in contact with water.
item.minium_me.energy.type.certus_quartz: Like quartz, Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.refined_glows: Increased power against Undead. It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light. When it lands on a block, it leaves a glowstone light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.refined_obsid: More powerful than Netherite. But can't give Wither effect.
item.minium_me.energy.type.ruby.desc: Increases damage against mobs that disable Freeze damage.
item.minium_me.energy.type.sapphire.desc: Penetrates projectile resistance and increases damage against mobs that can breathe underwater without being undead.
item.minium_me.energy.type.electrum.desc: Slows down Undead and makes everything else glow.
item.minium_me.energy.unusable: §7§oThis energy is not available in the current configuration
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_elytra.desc: Press the %s key during glide to boost using the blast wave (cooldown: %f seconds)
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_elytra.desc.u: §7§oBoosting is not possible because the key has not been set.
death.attack.minium_energy.item: %1$s were bathed in energy by %2$s using %3$s
enchantment.minium_me.stone_alchemy.desc: When you use RangeBreak, stones will no longer drop, but experience and ore will drop occasionally instead.
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_ston: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - Stone
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_neth: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - Netherrack
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_end_: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - End Stone
effect.minium_me.poison_heal.description: It nullifies damage caused by poison and restores strength when poisoned.
effect.minium_me.pickling_salt.descripti: Become damaged when exposed to water.
